Resource Profile: Location

Official URL: http://va.gov/fhir/StructureDefinition/Location Version: 1.4.10
Active as of 2025-04-18 Computable Name: Location

This StructureDefinition contains the maps for VistA file HOSPITAL LOCATION (44) to us-core-location.

​See also the FHIR Shorthand.

Use Case Overview

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: Appointment, Encounter: Inpatient Encounter, Encounter: Outpatient, Immunization Immunization... Show 8 more, MedicationDispense: Original, MedicationDispense: Partial, MedicationDispense: Refill, MedicationRequest: NonVA, Practitioner Role, Procedure: Radiology, Procedure: Surgery Location[OR] and Procedure: Surgery Procedure
  • CapabilityStatements using this Resource Profile: AMPL GUI, Lighthouse Clinical Health API, Debt Portal, Lung Cancer Screening and Lighthouse Patient Health API
